// Host receives in handleEvent():
if (!this.client.isHost) return;
const intent = payload as Intent;
switch(intent.type) {
  case 'moveTo': this.hostApplyMoveTo(from, intent.wx, intent.wy); break;
  case 'castAbility': this.hostApplyCast(from, intent); break;
  // ...
}
```

SHALLOW-MERGE GOTCHA: sharedState is `{...prev,...patch}` — only top-level keys merge. To update one unit's hp without resending all hp, keep `unitHp` as a Record and spread: `{ unitHp: { ...prev.unitHp, [id]: newHp } }`. Never nest deeper than 1 level in the patch or changes will be lost on merge.
